data.name: TextBox2.Text
data.value: Version 6.0(March 14, 2015) -UI changes -Support for High-DPI displays -Preview Aero window -Themes and settings window merged Version 5.0(November 2, 2014) -UI redesigned with flatter backgrounds to look better in Windows 8 -Fixed timer bug -Fixed Aero Adjust loading the wrong main color -New notification bar icon -Option to save the Aero tweaks you make into a separate file -Optimized weather downloading(now 2X as fast) -Get color from humidity -Get color from wind speed -Get color from webcam -Get color from cursor position(x and y axis) Version 4.0(July 25, 2014) -Complete rewrite -Bug fixes -Smaller Size -Get color from application icon -Less resource intensive, especially when getting average color -UI redesigned to look less crappy -New Icons -The color-averaging algorithm is more accurate -You can now save the changes you made as themes Version 3.0(November 6, 2012) -UI Changes Version 2.0(August 8, 2012) -MAJOR Bug fixes -Additional settings -Under the hood changes -Improved Icon -MAJOR UI Changes(UI improved massively, ice blue theme) -Notification Icon blends with other Windows 7 Icons -Option to clear settings -Themes Version 1.1(June 29, 2012) -MAJOR Bug fixes -Bug reports -Save Aero Settings to file -Get Aero Color from current window's icon -UI changes Version 1.0(December 20, 2011) -Initial Release
